data.description: Welcome to this charming home in the heart of Bethel Island, CA! This delightful property offers 2 bedrooms, 1 bathroom, and a host of features that make it a wonderful place to call home.  Step inside to discover new laminate flooring that adds a touch of elegance to the interior space. The recent interior paint gives the home a fresh and inviting atmosphere, while the upgraded electrical system and some new plumbing provide peace of mind for the new owner. The kitchen is a true highlight, boasting granite countertops and stainless steel appliances, including a sleek kitchen sink.  Outside, the ample front yard provides plenty of parking space, making it convenient for both residents and guests. Additionally, the property features a charming chicken coop, perfect for those with a green thumb or a love for farm-fresh eggs.  Located close to a boat launch, this home is a dream for water enthusiasts, offering easy access to the Delta for boating and other recreational activities. Furthermore, its proximity to downtown and restaurants ensures that entertainment and dining options are always within reach.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this lovely Bethel Island home your own. Schedule a showing today and experience the wonderful lifestyle this property has to offer! --
